(thirdQuint)Effects of Carboplatin and Gemcitabine on Stage IIIB Pleural Effusion and Stage IV Lung Cancer.

 Subjects enrolled in the study will be placed in one of two treatment arms.

 All subjects have a 50-50 chance of being placed into either treatment arm.

 Treatment Arm 1 will receive chemotherapy alone, Treatment Arm 2 will receive chemotherapy with dexamethasone given pre-treatment.

